reviewText: Nothing to write home to Walt about...better to see it in person.

Very nice DVD of Disneyland at Christmastime! You can enjoy the holiday parade without fighting crowds! Very nice quality DVD! Really puts you in a festive mood! The DVD also has Its A Small World holiday, and fireworks, and various sights around the park. I highly recommend!
Wonderful dvd. Excellent product & great service from seller.  Very  satisfied.
